{{Wireless embedded system |brand=Cisco |model=RV215W |upc=882658505324 |asin=B00AHSNQNS |fcc_date=08/01/2012 |manuf_country=China |is_manuf=No |manuf=CyberTAN |type=wireless router |fcc_id=N89-RV215W |ic_id=5005A-RV215W |pwr_v=12 |pwr_amp=1.5 |pwr_conn=barrel |cpu1_brand=Broadcom |cpu1_model=BCM5358UB0 |fla1=16 |fla1_brand=Macronix |fla1_model=MX25L12845EMI-10G |ram1=64 |ram1_brand=EtronTech |ram1_model=EM6AB160TSD-5G |expansion_if_types=USB 2.0 |expansion_usb_num=1 |jtag=yes,, 14-pin header,, unpopulated,, JC1 |serial=yes,, 5-pin header,, unpopulated,, JC2 |wi1_chip1_brand=Broadcom |wi1_chip1_model=BCM5358UB0 |wi1_802dot11_protocols=bgn |wi1_ant_conn=soldered |wi1_txchains=2 |wi1_rxchains=2 |wi1_sstreams=2 |eth_cpu=true |sw_cpu=true |lan_speed=100M |lan_ports=4 |wan_ports=1 |addl_chips=Dual USB High-Side Power Switch;Analog Integrations Corporation;AIC1526;;1;,,, |802dot11_protocols=bgn |default_ssid=ciscosb1 |default_ssid_regex=^ciscosb1$ |default_ip=192.168.1.1 |default_user=cisco |default_pass=cisco |oui=10:BD:18 |oui_eth=10:BD:18 }} "3763-12100501R" and the '''Cisco''' logo is silkscreened on the board in the FCC photos.
This device is using two [http://www.skyworksinc.com/Product.aspx?ProductID=958 '''Skyworks''' ('''SiGe''') SE2598L / 2598L 2.4GHz power amplfiers].
Per the FCC manual, the RF output power is 18 dBm. The default credentials are also from the FCC manual.
